title: Moses and Millenials - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/20/20
itunes:title: Moses and Millenials - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/20/20
description:
George Noory and Coast guest host Ian Punnett explore how younger generations can apply the leadership lessons of Moses who led the reluctant Israelites out of Egypt in the Bible to solve many of today's problems.
